data.description: Wonderful home at a wonderful price!  Basement level includes full bath and complete kitchen not included in square footage because of no heat.  City water bill is part of HOA fee.  Recent home inspection on file and repairs completed along with many updates.  Come enjoy the lovely view of the mountains as well as the privacy.  Close to all conveniences with close proximity to Hendersonville and Fletcher.  This home is spacious with multi-living purposes.  Welcome home!
